---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-slate-200/70 bg-graphite-950 text-white">
	<div class="site-container py-10 md:py-12">
		<div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.4fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] md:items-end">
			<div class="space-y-4">
				<div class="section-title text-slate-400" data-align="start">Contact</div>
				<p class="max-w-2xl text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">
					欢迎围绕研究议题、工程实现和安全相关项目进行交流。
				</p>
				<p class="max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300/78">
					站点采用 Astro + Tailwind CSS + Markdown/MDX 构建，持续沉淀项目、写作与长期技术记录。
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
				<a class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 px-5 py-4 no-underline transition hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10" href="/projects">
					<p class="font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-slate-400">Projects</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">查看精选项目</p>
				</a>
				<a class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 px-5 py-4 no-underline transition hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10" href="/posts">
					<p class="font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-slate-400">Posts</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">阅读最新文章</p>
				</a>
				<a class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/6 px-5 py-4 no-underline transition hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10" href="/rss.xml">
					<p class="font-mono text-[0.72rem] uppercase tracking-[0.26em] text-slate-400">RSS</p>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">订阅更新</p>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3 border-t border-white/10 pt-6 text-sm text-slate-400">
			<p>© {year} dkx. All rights reserved.</p>
			<p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500">Research / Build / Share</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</footer>
